# My Projects
Currently I'm developing a mod called AFM, which will include as many features as possible.

Along with it, I'm keeping this webpage updated, as the mod updates.

## AFM

### What is it?

AFM is, as stated before, a mod which will include everything I can think of. AFM stands for _Aritzh's First Mod_ (Not very original, I know), however, this might be a temporary name.

### Why make sucha an OmniMod?

It will help me make mods easily in the future. In addition, I might make some modding tutorials once AFM is finished, which makes me try to write the mod as cleanly as possible, so that it is easily readable.
